{"sn6.9:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 6.9 ","sn6.9:0.2":"1. Pathamavagga ","sn6.9:0.3":"Turubrahmasutta ","sn6.9:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn6.9:1.2":"Tena kho pana samayena kokaliko bhikkhu abadhiko hoti dukkhito balhagilano. ","sn6.9:1.3":"Atha kho turu paccekabrahma abhikkantaya rattiya abhikkantavanno kevalakappam jetavanam obhasetva yena kokaliko bhikkhu tenupasankami; upasankamitva vehasam thito kokalikam bhikkhum etadavoca: ","sn6.9:1.4":"“pasadehi, kokalika, sariputtamoggallanesu cittam. ","sn6.9:1.5":"Pesala sariputtamoggallana”ti. ","sn6.9:1.6":"“Kosi tvam, avuso”ti? ","sn6.9:1.7":"“Aham turu paccekabrahma”ti. ","sn6.9:1.8":"“Nanu tvam, avuso, bhagavata anagami byakato, atha kincarahi idhagato? ","sn6.9:1.9":"Passa, yavanca te idam aparaddhan”ti. ","sn6.9:2.1":"“Purisassa hi jatassa, ","sn6.9:2.2":"kuthari jayate mukhe; ","sn6.9:2.3":"Yaya chindati attanam, ","sn6.9:2.4":"balo dubbhasitam bhanam. ","sn6.9:3.1":"Yo nindiyam pasamsati, ","sn6.9:3.2":"Tam va nindati yo pasamsiyo; ","sn6.9:3.3":"Vicinati mukhena so kalim, ","sn6.9:3.4":"Kalina tena sukham na vindati. ","sn6.9:4.1":"Appamattako ayam kali, ","sn6.9:4.2":"Yo akkhesu dhanaparajayo; ","sn6.9:4.3":"Sabbassapi sahapi attana, ","sn6.9:4.4":"Ayameva mahantataro kali; ","sn6.9:4.5":"Yo sugatesu manam padosaye. ","sn6.9:5.1":"Satam sahassanam nirabbudanam, ","sn6.9:5.2":"Chattimsati panca ca abbudani; ","sn6.9:5.3":"Yamariyagarahi nirayam upeti, ","sn6.9:5.4":"Vacam mananca panidhaya papakan”ti. "}